## 🔹 PRACTICAL 5A – Maven Build Pipeline (IMPORTANT)

```groovy
pipeline {
    agent any

    tools {
        maven 'Maven'   // Make sure Maven is configured in Jenkins
    }

    stages {

        stage('Clone') {
            steps {
                git 'https://github.com/your-repo/maven-project.git'
            }
        }

        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                bat 'mvn clean compile'
            }
        }

        stage('Test') {
            steps {
                bat 'mvn test'
            }
        }

        stage('Package') {
            steps {
                bat 'mvn package'
            }
        }
    }

    post {
        success {
            echo 'Maven build successful!'
        }
        failure {
            echo 'Build failed!'
        }
    }
}
```

